{"Id":480,"LanguageCodes":["zh","zho"],"Name":"zho-majian","Author":"Ma Jian","Language":"Chinese(simplified)","Description":"Chinese(simplified)","Direction":"ltr","Source":"http://tanzil.net","Translations":[{"SurahNumber":89,"VerseNumber":24,"Text":"他将说：但愿我在世的时候曾行善事。"},{"SurahNumber":89,"VerseNumber":25,"Text":"在那日，任何人，不用他的那种刑罚惩治别人；"},{"SurahNumber":89,"VerseNumber":26,"Text":"任何人，不用他的那种束缚束缚别人。"},{"SurahNumber":89,"VerseNumber":27,"Text":"安定的灵魂啊！"},{"SurahNumber":89,"VerseNumber":28,"Text":"你应当喜悦地，被喜悦地归於你的主。"},{"SurahNumber":89,"VerseNumber":29,"Text":"你应当入在我的众仆里；"},{"SurahNumber":89,"VerseNumber":30,"Text":"你应当入在我的乐园里。"},{"SurahNumber":90,"VerseNumber":1,"Text":"我以这个地方盟誓"},{"SurahNumber":90,"VerseNumber":2,"Text":"你将在那里，不受羁束"},{"SurahNumber":90,"VerseNumber":3,"Text":"我以一个父亲和他所生的子孙盟誓，"},{"SurahNumber":90,"VerseNumber":4,"Text":"我确已把人创造在苦难里。"},{"SurahNumber":90,"VerseNumber":5,"Text":"他以为任何人都不能制裁他吗？"},{"SurahNumber":90,"VerseNumber":6,"Text":"他说：我花费了许多财产！"},{"SurahNumber":90,"VerseNumber":7,"Text":"他以为任何人都没有看见他吗？"},{"SurahNumber":90,"VerseNumber":8,"Text":"难道我没有为他创造两只眼睛、"},{"SurahNumber":90,"VerseNumber":9,"Text":"一条舌头、两片嘴唇，"},{"SurahNumber":90,"VerseNumber":10,"Text":"并指示他两条明显的道路吗？"},{"SurahNumber":90,"VerseNumber":11,"Text":"他怎麽不超越山径呢？"},{"SurahNumber":90,"VerseNumber":12,"Text":"你怎能知道超越山径是什麽事？"},{"SurahNumber":90,"VerseNumber":13,"Text":"是释放奴隶，"},{"SurahNumber":90,"VerseNumber":14,"Text":"或在饥荒日赈济"},{"SurahNumber":90,"VerseNumber":15,"Text":"亲戚的孤儿，"},{"SurahNumber":90,"VerseNumber":16,"Text":"或困穷的贫民；"},{"SurahNumber":90,"VerseNumber":17,"Text":"同时，他是一个信道而且行善，并以坚忍相勉，以慈悯相助者。"},{"SurahNumber":90,"VerseNumber":18,"Text":"这等人是幸福的。"},{"SurahNumber":90,"VerseNumber":19,"Text":"不信我的迹象者，是薄命的，"},{"SurahNumber":90,"VerseNumber":20,"Text":"他们将被关在火狱里。"}]}